data.description: *Have agent check disclosures*INSTANT EQUITY! MOTIVATED SELLERS! SELLER IS OFFERING A CONCESSION AT PURCHASE PRICE AND A HOME WARRANTY. Beautifully updated tri-level with a large yard and garage that backs up to a private wooded area in the rear. This home is located in the Seadenville Subdivision that is a very inviting family community. One of the highly desired daycare centers (Lil Graduates) is just around the corner and the Anchor Bay school district is one of the top districts in all of the state. The area is a very private environment with plenty of entertainment and activities within walking distance, including but not limited to, bowling, grocery stores, fast food restaurants, movie theatre, fitness, retail, and so much more! Roof is 2016 and place was remodeled in 2019.  Due to having a toddler and pets, showing times are very limited and special showing arrangements are made.
